Program: Omnibus
Title: Children of Conflict
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lxd
Last Broadcast Date: 25 May 1999
2 million children have died and 6 million have been injured due to war in the last 10 years. A look at the plight of children touched by armed conflicts around the world. Contributors include Olara Otunnu, UN special envoy.